5863dd22e9507798b6c4fdc2f2dc7b217cd449f0fe6253a2aac57726c82b04c28b49b82c325060d64e460b77fc59c95971b91922c946b9262dac660fe314cfdf  0001-knewstuff-Fix-link-list-dialog-for-installation-button.patch
"
